==Swedish==
===Idiom===
'''[[skräda]] [[ord#Swedish|ord]]en'''

#to express oneself very carefully and diplomaticly, to refuse to say anything which may be considered harmful or disrespectful no matter how true.

====Usage notes====
Usually used in the negative sense, "att inte skräda orden", i.e. to be frank and outspoken; not afraid of hurting other peoples feelings.

